title: Authorizes the city of New York to reconvey its interest in certain real property acquired by in rem tax foreclosure in the borough of Bronx to former owner St. Peter's Lutheran Church
actClause: AN ACT authorizing the city of New York to reconvey its interest in certain real property acquired by in rem tax foreclosure in the borough of Bronx to former owner St. Peter's Lutheran Church, notwithstanding expiration of the two year period within which application may be made to the city to release its interest in property thus acquired; Block No. 2285, Lot No. 73 on tax map for the borough of Bronx
